      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/10a32d30813ab85f8g0175ac?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=15665&rangeEnd=15730"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300080567_17_3505-3600",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "3505-3600",
      "markText": "在马尔蒂瓦克的早期阶段，人们就发现瓶颈在于提出问题的程序。马尔蒂瓦克能够解决人类的任何困难，只要——只要能问出有意义的问题。但随着知识累积的速度越来越快，要找到有意义的问题也变得越来越困难。",
      "totalCount": 532,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300080567&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=3505&rangeEnd=3600",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/10a32d30813ab85f8g0175ac?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=3505&rangeEnd=3600"
    },
    {
